REMD using PMEMD for amoeba must use 2 or more cores for each replica.
To turn on Bussi algorithm, set ntt=4,
To use Respa, set dt(=0.00025) to be the time step for valence updates. 
Every nrespa*dt time step, nonbonded interactions will be updated once.
nstlim, numexchg, ntpr, ntwr, ntave, nscm, ntwx... have to be an integer multiple of nrespa.
